  "description": "# Cairo · CAI\n\nUmm al-Dunya; mega-city on the Nile. One of the largest maps in the collection, spanning greater Cairo from Giza across the river to Nasr City and Heliopolis.\n\n## Coverage\n\n<table style=\"width: auto\">\n<tr><td><strong>Region</strong></td><td>Greater Cairo, Egypt (EG)</td></tr>\n<tr><td><strong>Bounding Box</strong></td><td>30.80, 29.80 → 31.85, 30.28</td></tr>\n<tr><td><strong>Playable Area</strong></td><td>~5,410 km²</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n## Population Summary\n\n<table style=\"width: auto\">\n<tr><td><strong>Metro Population</strong></td><td align=\"right\">22,000,000</td></tr>\n<tr><td><strong>Total Modeled Demand</strong></td><td align=\"right\">1,509,805</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n## Map Statistics\n\n<table style=\"width: auto\">\n<tr><td><strong>Buildings Indexed</strong></td><td align=\"right\">1,524,814</td></tr>\n<tr><td><strong>Demand Points</strong></td><td align=\"right\">1,248</td></tr>\n<tr><td><strong>Population Nodes</strong></td><td align=\"right\">14,487</td></tr>\n<tr><td><strong>Median Commute Distance</strong></td><td align=\"right\">18.1 km</td></tr>\n<tr><td><strong>Mean Commute Distance</strong></td><td align=\"right\">24.2 km</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n## Additional Features\n\n- **Building Collision** — A buildings index of 1,524,814 structures is included — the largest in the collection — providing in-game collision geometry for all non-filtered buildings.\n- **Road & Runway Overlays** — Road network plus runway/taxiway geometry are bundled, covering Cairo International Airport and surface routing across the metro.",
